  <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
  <p>Habsy Technologies is pleased to submit this proposal for the provision of our AI-powered Habsy Business Card Manager app to <b data-bind="companyName"><%= proposal.companyName || 'Company Name' %></b> for their team. This proposal outlines the features, pricing, deliverables, terms, and conditions for onboarding your members onto our platform.</p>
  <p><strong>Use Case:</strong> Habsy empowers your team to maximize ROI from exhibitions, meetings, and field visits by instantly capturing business card details on the spot. Users can scan business cards and add/sync contacts, and the app automatically deduplicates entries to ensure a clean, contact base. The contacts can then be exported for efficient follow-up, turning every connection into a qualified lead for your sales pipeline.</p>
  <ul style="margin: 0 0 0 18px;">
    <li><strong>Fast capture anywhere:</strong> AI scanning, batch processing, and event badge QR scanning.</li>
    <li><strong>Context at the moment of scan:</strong> tags, custom fields, voice notes, and follow-up reminders.</li>
    <li><strong>Reliable data quality:</strong> automatic deduplication and standardized fields for easy search.</li>
    <li><strong>Works in the real world:</strong> multi-language support and offline capture with auto-sync.</li>
    <li><strong>Ready for action:</strong> export to Excel (CSV) or VCF for campaigns</li>
  </ul>

